<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٧-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي عِصْمَةُ بْنُ عِصَامٍ حَدَّثَنَا حَنْبَلٌ قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ يَقُولُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَأَكْرَهُ السَّوَادَ لِأَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ <span class="c4">[قَالَ]</span> :<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">((وَجَنِّبُوهُ السَّوَادَ)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَلَا يَعْجِبُنِي الْخِضَابُ بِهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>